To create a collection:
Click the + on the home page.
Type in a name for the collection in the Name field.
Type in a description in the Description field.
Click the Color dropdown menu to color code your collection for display on the home page.
Click Save. Click Cancel to start over.

Each user can create up to 100 collections.
